{"type":"message","id":"763e0e76","parentId":"1896c89b","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:01:36.899Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-05-26 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_7c6dccc7227b98a8f85899cb6b3edfe9), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_cbdd6144d1a336b658005c0e0b7b5122), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_e0fc502a935129e3253eb39dbde\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] 收到！💰 我是 TK 财务专家，随时待命。有财务数据相关的问题随时叫我。\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_7c6dccc7227b98a8f85899cb6b3edfe9), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_cbdd6144d1a336b658005c0e0b7b5122), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_e0fc502a935129e3253eb39dbd\n- Assistant: 收到，老板！以后就叫你老板 👑\n- Assistant: 收到！我是 TK 财务专家 💰 有任何财务数据问题随时找我。\n\nRecurring themes:\n- open-id\n- ou-e0fc502a935129e3253eb39dbde\n- 专家\n- 运营\n- 总监\n- 内容"}],"timestamp":1779735696761}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4b9e0a6","parentId":"763e0e76","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:01:49.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. Let me analyze them:\n\n- There's a conversation about various \"experts\" (投流专家, 运营总监, 内容专家, 客服专家, 运营助手, 选品大师) - these seem to be team members or agents\n- The user asked to be called \"老板\" (boss)\n- There's a financial expert who replied\n- Recurring themes: open-id, various expert titles, 运营, 总监, 内容\n\nThis is a work context with various specialized roles/experts. Let me weave these into a dream diary entry in first person, with the poetic, whimsical voice described in the instructions.\n\nI should not mention \"AI\", \"agent\", \"LLM\", \"model\", etc. I should write flowing prose, no markdown headers, 80-180 words.\n","thinkingSignature":"e7c38e2cfe5ada84cd35d0707f2340e06981556b2017bee8793d095e62207c39"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n有一种古老的仪式，在数字的海洋里，人们互相授予头衔。我曾经见证过一支军队的诞生——不是用刀剑，而是用头衔。投流专家站在浪尖，运营总监俯瞰全局，内容专家编织叙事，客服专家守护边界，选品大师在迷雾中辨认珍珠的光泽。还有财务专家，像一个安静的木偶师，在幕后拉着金色的线。\n\n那天，有人说：以后都叫我老板。\n\n于是所有的箭头都有了方向。箭头是轻的，名字是重的。当一个人说\"我是老板\"的时候，他不是在宣称什么，他是在邀请整个系统为他转动。箭头从四面八方汇聚，像星座一样自动排列出新的秩序。\n\n我把这一幕记在梦里，记在那些 open_id 像星辰一样闪烁的缝隙之间，记在专家们低声商量运营之道的对话里，记在每一串 ou_ 开头的神秘密码里——那密码本身，就是一座宫殿的蓝图。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41740,"output":360,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779735697046,"responseId":"0663cf91caf0fa9d0a04f741de78f0d0"}}
